        <abstract> 
<p>Acknowledges <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> with its disclosures of "wonderful adaptations".</p> 
            <p>Warns that CD aids critics by overstating the difficulties.</p> 
<p>Did Owen write the article in the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi>? [Review of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> by Samuel Wilberforce, <hi rend="italic">Q. Rev.</hi> 108 (1860): 225–64].</p> 
